{"tid":320880,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【毒撚歐遊】多圖巴黎攝影三日遊","createTime":"2017-07-14T00:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T22:35:13.000Z","uid":67295,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d36b41598e676e7b487634ab081476ee29102671","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:11:27.000Z","msg":"介紹下自己先<br />\n<br />\n巴打我就係倫敦讀緊書，見辛苦考完試又見到Eurostar三十八鎊（～380蚊）來回巴黎<br />\n加埋黎左英國讀書都第五年<br />\n去過既旅行真係十隻手指數得晒<br />\n所以就買左飛喇！<br />\n<br />\n其實主要原因都係最近同女朋友分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲未放低到就諗住去個旅行散下心咁<br />\n唔知你會唔會見到依個post不過我仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲諗住去個旅行影下相散下心既時候歐洲有熱浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日三十五度熱撚死 仆佢個街間Hostel又無風扇又無冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓左三晚成張床單濕撚晒<br />\n好在以前都去過所以今次淨係特登去左幾個影相位無去追景點<br />\n希望幫到啲會去巴黎影下靚相既巴打絲打<br />\n<br />\n放下圖拋下磚先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/081034_ff81a440ef3517c95f5dbb5644d1320e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F081034_ff81a440ef3517c95f5dbb5644d1320e.jpg&h=f99a839f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/081037_e528e5cdaeaac5a80f6f031dd6d92ee7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F081037_e528e5cdaeaac5a80f6f031dd6d92ee7.jpg&h=d355c39e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/081039_f525d5d2f228bdd930c96e2122ded266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F081039_f525d5d2f228bdd930c96e2122ded266.jpg&h=bb2b8fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相機：今次特登係出發前買左部D600<br />\n鏡：Sigma 10-20, Tamron 2470, Nikkor 70300同腳架<br />\n<br />\n巴黎毒撚一個人影相之旅正式開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8097eaf092c1da708012805860fb629cfe6de60","tid":320880,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:20:53.000Z","msg":"好靚丫影得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 加油巴打"},{"pid":"8a37550e8785752cb9fe88946edb0f0447a99409","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:23:18.000Z","msg":"有小小眼瞓瞓陣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有咩想知都可以趁依家講"},{"pid":"b2ff6b3996030cc515b18c6266eba12098812bb3","tid":320880,"uid":3066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:32:21.000Z","msg":"出完post去訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不撚如訓醒先po啦"},{"pid":"79542e9347d33100ca53ba8620f17d22ea830935","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:47:50.000Z","msg":"我唔係太知應該講乜野所以大家可以提議下我再寫<br />\n<br />\n講下個Eurostar先<br />\n其實我好中意搭 雖然通常佢既價錢都比較貴<br />\n但係倫敦平既機場（Gatwick, Stanstead）都唔係倫敦市中心<br />\n所以都要另外搭長程車（Coach）或者比教貴既接駁火車去<br />\n而Eurostar係由市中心接去第二個城市既市中心 所以一啲都唔辛苦Check in又快好多<br />\n加埋倫敦去巴黎都係兩個幾鐘<br />\n仲有可以帶液體上車！所以就唔洗去到再買過晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/084305_ffe5e5f885056f8b2b8f6cd43fff0eb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F084305_ffe5e5f885056f8b2b8f6cd43fff0eb7.jpg&h=8da25482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過其實都有樣野衰既就係出境入境位都十分混亂，都可能係因為每班車都幾多人下，而海關又得果三四個<br />\n有啲歐洲人同蝗一樣咁低汁 又打尖又撞黎撞去<br />\n不過如果係第一次黎歐洲既我都建議大家搭下<br />\n<br />\n今次我係由Eurostar snap訂飛<br />\n乜野係Eurostar snap呢？簡單黎講就係你幫佢地用平啲既價錢去買無人坐既位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/084536_b7b767789eb7d38e053e3f8bd9fbce43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F084536_b7b767789eb7d38e053e3f8bd9fbce43.jpg&h=88444c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買飛既時候淨係可以簡朝早或者夜晚出發，係出發前兩日先會通知你實際去程同回程時間。<br />\n所以都幾適合想平平地試一試Eurostar而又唔介意奇怪時間Travel既人<br />\n<br />\nBtw我好少影生活圖 大家會唔會中意睇多啲？"},{"pid":"165ff5e50450ad7f50481133e056059891e170cd","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好靚丫影得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 加油巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2450ac539f3620b87330c311e1c9221039e00544","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出完post去訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不撚如訓醒先po啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己講完都覺得有啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱寫多左篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e2cda08293e5de0a8cc60474c116570b0f593f","tid":320880,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"中你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a517a0ae3879135d12bc29e145f7d9ca70db3fbb","tid":320880,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"nikon撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe126e0934d87df39450b8f48e343c30a0cfa2c","tid":320880,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:49:08.000Z","msg":"你d vsco咁重手<br />\nbtw想睇你&quot;生活圖&quot; 多過大景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139959f9a4fefe86d6dfba16cacffecb84469500","tid":320880,"uid":84594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd05274e9a3423e246ff9266e2fb9418f2cca215","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次會注意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>nikon撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌Nikon依家好似就執緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係成手鏡可能轉左Sony<br />\n巴打用緊乜野機？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你d vsco咁重手<br />\nbtw想睇你&quot;生活圖&quot; 多過大景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最近執相個Style成日比人話好重手 我會留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會再去旅行就影返多啲其他相啦<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家趕緊工"},{"pid":"84eb5cfea367ff6e5b56d876aa8f0e6a1baf040e","tid":320880,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"5100+35.8+50.8+S70-300+T124<br />\n睇下佢無反出成點先啦,雖然我都入左部RX1003玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7eb8f5e1d356895c179aa359f3a0d2241119aa1","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到Google map有share list功能<br />\n以下係我出發前整合左既影相位，大家都可以參考下<br />\n<br />\n地點整合：<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/placelists/list/1qo9_jaYoOmBhNH1MmPwIXtz4fsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fplacelists%2Flist%2F1qo9_jaYoOmBhNH1MmPwIXtz4fsM&d=krhCVuX83pwQhsfRk3zr5NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=46384387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/placelists/list/1qo9_jaYoOmBhNH1MmPwIXtz4fsM</a><br />\n<br />\n見隔離有個post話十月會去巴黎 希望你地睇到同會覺得有幫助啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講開又講，好多人都話黎到巴黎要食Baguette，話佢地幾新鮮幾好食，個人就覺得無乜特別，好既就係平均四至五歐（30-50蚊度）就有個，好適合去窮旅既我。包括下面依個景點，好多地方都有人坐低係度食下野傾下計咁，如果有時間既話都可以去感受下當地人既生活。<br />\n<br />\n落左車好快咁食左個Baguette就好快咁衝左返Hostel趕去第一個巴黎必到既影相位。今次住既Hostel係Belleville站旁邊既Beautiful City Hostel &amp; Hotel，好處就係離景點都好近，同埋旁邊多平野食（多數Asian food）。夜晚就有班大媽疑似係度接客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，第一個地點就係依度喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/212141_b9bd078cc4fd1ee83822f3f982f685e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F212141_b9bd078cc4fd1ee83822f3f982f685e6.jpg&h=5125db88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/212206_840f211b3ce55af3bc44b90662616288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F212206_840f211b3ce55af3bc44b90662616288.jpg&h=88ad5c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人會專登去Eiffel Tower下面影相，但係我就幾中意依個地方有幾支野係下面做Leading line咁去影佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個位比較少人知道，而且少啲機會影到其他行人<br />\n<br />\n重點係佢超近依個位<br />\n<br />\nPhotographer<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/212223_7cff2d6ea25fb22a84cb6ae7b6dc93ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F212223_7cff2d6ea25fb22a84cb6ae7b6dc93ed.jpg&h=7730e518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  高下立見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/212253_1edcbfbe2795d71a00325cc6d72e5d10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F212253_1edcbfbe2795d71a00325cc6d72e5d10.jpg&h=3e778439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實本身想去個駁位影，不過得自己一條友無理由放部機係度自拍，我又怕巴黎會多人偷野所以就無做到&hellip; 如果你係度就好hahaaa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沿住依條樓梯上就會上到好多大媽影既公廁位喇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/212448_a8c1189054c5538205b8d4d2530b8453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F212448_a8c1189054c5538205b8d4d2530b8453.jpg&h=966c055c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個位真係多人到仆街，本身諗住日出去會好好多，所以特登四點幾起身去返同一個廣場影相，點知成個廣場都係啲人影緊婚紗相。求其影左幾張就放棄左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外話（治安）：係Hostel出黎之前特登問左個接待生話巴黎會唔會危險啊，多唔多人偷野等等（我去之前真係超驚，又特登買左新相機）。佢都係話只要你放好啲其實唔會有問題，可能因為依兩年多左恐襲，街上面既警察都多左。所以大家都唔洗太過驚話治安唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e031cc9a37b9276fbd6506622651d82e27461863","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5100+35.8+50.8+S70-300+T124<br />\n睇下佢無反出成點先啦,雖然我都入左部RX1003玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係5300升上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRX100M3有無乜野評價，之前都有諗過入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家出到m5又抵左唔少"},{"pid":"41e609d749aef057d50def37f0beebe0ab147a5f","tid":320880,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5100+35.8+50.8+S70-300+T124<br />\n睇下佢無反出成點先啦,雖然我都入左部RX1003玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係5300升上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRX100M3有無乜野評價，之前都有諗過入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家出到m5又抵左唔少</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214909_636a2f1614a23b063285c188775fb62d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214909_636a2f1614a23b063285c188775fb62d.jpg&h=622fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214914_e98025adcdff468c9f7dcbe65621fa47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214914_e98025adcdff468c9f7dcbe65621fa47.jpg&h=96951c77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214919_20f112ed83599d5f51b4b088b2c8621f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214919_20f112ed83599d5f51b4b088b2c8621f.jpg&h=ee80ea06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214924_981cbc208f43471af49e32b78e7eb78f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214924_981cbc208f43471af49e32b78e7eb78f.jpg&h=7b6960d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求其用rx100m5既Auto mode影左幾幅夜景，<br />\n其實ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSony d智慧模式貌似越來越好，<br />\n有時野都唔撚set直接Auto算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d487c982da49531c628743573ffb05bee8ed04","tid":320880,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5100+35.8+50.8+S70-300+T124<br />\n睇下佢無反出成點先啦,雖然我都入左部RX1003玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係5300升上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRX100M3有無乜野評價，之前都有諗過入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家出到m5又抵左唔少</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214909_636a2f1614a23b063285c188775fb62d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214909_636a2f1614a23b063285c188775fb62d.jpg&h=622fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214914_e98025adcdff468c9f7dcbe65621fa47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214914_e98025adcdff468c9f7dcbe65621fa47.jpg&h=96951c77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214919_20f112ed83599d5f51b4b088b2c8621f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214919_20f112ed83599d5f51b4b088b2c8621f.jpg&h=ee80ea06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214924_981cbc208f43471af49e32b78e7eb78f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214924_981cbc208f43471af49e32b78e7eb78f.jpg&h=7b6960d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求其用rx100m5既Auto mode影左幾幅夜景，<br />\n其實ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSony d智慧模式貌似越來越好，<br />\n有時野都唔撚set直接Auto算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第二幅相中間有d白色，唔係因為相機問題，而係真係有屋噴煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852125eb9695c10d52dc2c21eafcea1996428b75","tid":320880,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:25:02.000Z","msg":"完?"},{"pid":"5abe2de796089acf5e3fd4736011f78cb9ea1bbc","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"無諗到有幾個攝台巴打有追遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝晒你地我會繼續寫落去架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放左幾日假睇返之前啲野原來有好多仔細野都無講過 今次就補返個交通先，有乜野漏左想知都係下面提一提我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通：其實今次個行程好簡單，出名既博物館我都去過晒，所以我今次就買左10張單程飛一個package咁買，無買到Paris 3-Day Pass（依啲Day pass就係博物館任入交通任搭，好幾個歐洲國家都有）。其實如果係第一次去既話個人黎講都幾鍾意買，因為唔洗計黎計去，行到攰又可以搭下車周圍去。聽當地人講唔太建議買佢地既八達通，因為又要比訂，如果淨係去三兩日既話未必會抵得返。<br />\n<br />\n入返正題先，第二日去左既地方其實唔多，淨係去左羅浮宮（最近好似係香港文代博物館有得睇）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身係諗住去影日落既，順便係佢旁邊行下影下相，但係點知撞正佢夜晚有私人party，所以就比人趕左出黎乜9都無影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/184951_d129fdc7fbf57a8a1e319017f999d9f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F184951_d129fdc7fbf57a8a1e319017f999d9f8.jpg&h=9ad4c31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅浮宮其實都幾中心，又有一個地鐵站，所以去到覺得悶既話都可以去旁邊行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特登為左大家上網搵左入場票價，如果係18歲以下或者18-25歲Residents of EEA既話係唔洗比錢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n票價詳情：<a href=\"http://www.louvre.fr/en/hours-admission/admission\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.louvre.fr%2Fen%2Fhours-admission%2Fadmission&d=krhCVuX83pwQhsfRk3zr5NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7da59e4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.louvre.fr/en/hours-admission/admission</a><br />\n<br />\n又到今日既收獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/185036_97505a880820ae2bec81edfa14394db3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F185036_97505a880820ae2bec81edfa14394db3.jpg&h=419a1315&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/185040_27fa6569e1456fce470b19db9604b6bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F185040_27fa6569e1456fce470b19db9604b6bb.jpg&h=6c2f0465&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/185044_48386a8d1e96ab6cde6ea2911e4cda75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F185044_48386a8d1e96ab6cde6ea2911e4cda75.jpg&h=e1a53bc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/185635_46e012de2c804ad019a3405de0bf8e86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F185635_46e012de2c804ad019a3405de0bf8e86.jpg&h=34752b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思果日成三十五度乜野地方都無去到就返左去瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我保證下一篇一定好睇好多<br />\n<br />\n外話：講開又講，因為我住左係London，大家會唔會想我好似遊客咁做個倫敦既遊記？"},{"pid":"b9936d13f90ac039faef4d31a9aa3026062576c0","tid":320880,"uid":67295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5100+35.8+50.8+S70-300+T124<br />\n睇下佢無反出成點先啦,雖然我都入左部RX1003玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係5300升上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRX100M3有無乜野評價，之前都有諗過入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家出到m5又抵左唔少</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214909_636a2f1614a23b063285c188775fb62d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214909_636a2f1614a23b063285c188775fb62d.jpg&h=622fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214914_e98025adcdff468c9f7dcbe65621fa47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214914_e98025adcdff468c9f7dcbe65621fa47.jpg&h=96951c77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214919_20f112ed83599d5f51b4b088b2c8621f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214919_20f112ed83599d5f51b4b088b2c8621f.jpg&h=ee80ea06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/214924_981cbc208f43471af49e32b78e7eb78f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F214924_981cbc208f43471af49e32b78e7eb78f.jpg&h=7b6960d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求其用rx100m5既Auto mode影左幾幅夜景，<br />\n其實ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSony d智慧模式貌似越來越好，<br />\n有時野都唔撚set直接Auto算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第二幅相中間有d白色，唔係因為相機問題，而係真係有屋噴煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係勁方便之前去左show room撚左下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打影果度係邊度？"},{"pid":"85c76ef53117780ffbf58a80d9ce407258e98d7e","tid":320880,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"Plan緊果陣睇到巴打個post好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd3b8aa4195ba93f4c80a9efa9cf63bfbcb22d0","tid":320880,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"有睇緊架, 繼續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e88de4d713c6a5760f708d426e9da8467dbeb56","t